\

*$ "Beg. R.E." + "Net Income" - "Dividends" = "End R.E." $*
\
- Debit balance $-->$ Lifetime Earnings $>$ Lifetime losses & Dividends

- Credit balance $-->$ Lifetime Earnings $<$ Lifetime losses & Dividends
