== Stock Dividends
\

1. Proportional distribution of stock to shareholders
2. Increase Share Capital and decrease Retained Earnings
  - Total equity is unchanged
3. Reasons stock dividends are distributed
  - Continue dividends, but conserve cash
  - Reduce market price of shares
