== Preferred Share Dividends
\
1. Paid dividends before common shareholders
2. Expressed as an annual dollar figure or as a percentage of the share's stated value
  - May be cumulative
3. Passed dividends are owed to preferred shareholders 
  - In arrears


*The Process of Stock/Share Dividends* \
\

